== Review Sets

Review sets mirror the storage topology under `docs/cold_storage/reviews/`.
Concern events that describe the steering impact of a review wave use
`source_type=review_set` and `source_id=REVSET-*` to anchor here.
Navigate from event to review set to individual review documents.

